Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_design_netlisttype(25.10)                  init_design_netlisttype(25.10)

Name
       init_design_netlisttype

Syntax
        init_design_netlisttype <netlist_source>

       Type: String

       Default: Verilog

       Specifies the source of the design netlist. You can specify either Ver-
       ilog  or OA. The init_design_netlisttype variable replaces the previous
       rda_Input(ui_netlisttype) configuration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies Verilog as the source  of  the
                design netlist.

                set init_design_netlisttype {Verilog}

